snippet.title: GlueFO
snippet.description: GlueFO Collect the tiny orbs and use them to shoot at the big orbs until there are only tiny orbs left.

snippet.title: Mole's Quest 2
snippet.description: Mole's Quest 2 Look for the animal that is responsible for the polution. Destroy opponents and find the solution.

snippet.title: Pimp My Ride
snippet.description: Pimp My Ride Beef up your rust heap by picking up pimp coins around the track. You have two minutes.

snippet.title: T-Rex Rampage: Prehistoric Pizza
snippet.description: T-Rex Rampage: Prehistoric Pizza Play a hungry T-Rex dino. Destroy the city and find slices of pizza to survive.

snippet.title: The Guardian 2
snippet.description: The Guardian 2 Adventure inspired by Zelda. Find the Lantern of Nightmare and free the people of Reverie.

snippet.title: Magi: The Fallen World
snippet.description: Magi: The Fallen World RPG adventure. Pick a character and look for quests, explore dungeons and fight powerful monsters.

snippet.title: Toad Trouble
snippet.description: Toad Trouble Platform adventure. Swing through all of the levels using your tongue to swing and collect all flies.

snippet.title: Transylvania
snippet.description: Transylvania Point 'n click story in which your task is to help Mr. Potato with escaping from scary Transylvania.

snippet.title: Gravistation
snippet.description: Gravistation Help the robot to find the exit of each level by rotating the entire level looking for a safe path.
